Description: Find where bulk RNA-seq data lies on a single-cell pseudotime 
  trajectory. Uses a fast, understandable correlation based approach. Can be 
  used to improve bulk DE, or understand real timepoints in SC from 
  timeseries bulk data.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
